## Project Structure

- This is a frontend-only project
- No server or backend components should be added
- Static site deployment on Netlify
- Using shadcn components and Tailwind CSS for theming

## Build and Package Management

- Use Bun exclusively for all operations:
  - Package management (bun install)
  - Running scripts (bun run)
  - Building (bun run build)
- Do not use npm or yarn commands
- Avoid suggesting npm-specific configurations or flags

## Deployment

- Netlify deployment should use Bun for all build steps
- Required Bun installation in build environment
- Build command should use Bun paths explicitly
